{
  "text": "The results of the meta-analysis provide empirical evidence that study characteristics related to the alternative globalization indices employed exert systematic impact on the estimated effect of globalization on capital taxation. In particular, studies employing globalization measures based on actual trade flows or on capital account restrictions typically report negative estimation of this effect whereas studies based on the KOF index of globalization developed by [CITATION_1] typically report a positive effect.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "14900094"
  },
